# E2E Testing Policy

Add or update Playwright E2E tests when changes affect user-visible behavior.

- Add a new E2E test for new user-facing behavior.
- Add a regression E2E test for bug fixes.
- Prefer stable selectors (`getByRole`, labels, placeholders) over brittle CSS selectors.
- Keep tests deterministic and isolated (clear/setup state per test).
- Run relevant E2E tests before finishing implementation.

Do not require E2E tests for:
- docs-only changes
- pure refactors with no behavior change
- internal config/tooling changes with no user-facing impact

If E2E is skipped, explicitly state why it is not reasonable.
